User 1 refers to the specific user with the unique identifier '1' in the access_logs table; 
Implementation language refers to the programming language in which the algorithm is written. 
Average runtime refers to the mean execution time of the algorithm's benchmark result.

sql:
SELECT algorithm_name, complexity_analysis
FROM algorithms
ORDER BY algorithm_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
